---
import { Section, Heading, IconLink } from 'kc-astro-shared-theme';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/custom.css';
// Import client list data
import clientList from '../data/client-list.json';
// Get Content Collection
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
const portfolioPosts = await getCollection('portfolioPosts');
---

<Layout title="Ken Chase - Web Design and Development Services" description="Professional web design and WordPress development services in Ottawa. Custom websites, design systems, and ongoing support for government, non-profit, and business clients across Canada.">
  <Section classList="kc-region--lg kc-region--inverted-light">
    <Heading tag="h1" size="h2">Web Design and Development Services</Heading>
    <p>I specialize in creating websites that feel authentic to your mission and effortless for your users, combining thoughtful design with well-crafted development. From our first brainstorming session to long after your site goes live, I'm your dedicated partner in making your digital presence truly shine.</p>
  </Section>

  <Section classList="kc-region--lg">
    <div class="grid" data-layout="50-50">
      <Heading tag="h2" size="h2">Web Design</Heading>
      <div class="content flow prose">
        <p>Every organization has a unique story to tell, and your website should reflect that. I craft custom designs that capture your brand's personality while prioritizing user experience and accessibility.</p>
        <p>Through collaborative discovery sessions and iterative design processes, we'll create a digital presence that feels authentically yours and connects meaningfully with your audience.</p>
        <p>Whether you need a complete redesign or a fresh new site, I handle everything from initial concepts through launch and training. My goal is to make the process as seamless as possible for you, so you can focus on what you do best.</p>
        <IconLink href="mailto:hello@kenchase.com?subject=Ken Chase web design services">Contact me about web design</IconLink>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
  <Section classList="kc-region--lg">
    <div class="grid" data-layout="50-50">
      <Heading tag="h2" size="h2">WordPress Development</Heading>
      <div class="content flow prose">
        <p>I build tailored WordPress solutions that fit your exact needsâ€”from custom themes and plugins to complex functionality that makes your site work exactly how you envision it.</p>
        <p>I also work with modern frameworks like Astro for lightning-fast, content-focused sites.</p>
        <p>Whether you need advanced search features, custom post types, or seamless integrations, I create clean, maintainable code that grows with your organization.</p>
        <IconLink href="mailto:hello@kenchase.com?subject=Ken Chase WordPress services">Contact me about WordPress</IconLink>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
  <Section classList="kc-region--lg">
    <div class="grid" data-layout="50-50">
      <Heading tag="h2" size="h2">Figma Design Systems</Heading>
      <div class="content flow prose">
        <p>Consistency builds trust, and design systems build consistency. I develop comprehensive design systems that ensure your brand looks and feels cohesive across all touchpoints.</p>
        <p>From color palettes and typography to component libraries in Figma, I create scalable design foundations that streamline future projects and empower your team to maintain brand integrity.</p>
        <IconLink href="mailto:hello@kenchase.com?subject=Ken Chase design systems">Contact me about design systems</IconLink>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
  <Section classList="kc-region--lg">
    <div class="grid" data-layout="50-50">
      <Heading tag="h2" size="h2">Website Support and Maintenance</Heading>
      <div class="content flow prose">
        <p>Your website is an investment that deserves ongoing care. I provide reliable maintenance services that keep your site secure, updated, and performing at its best.</p>
        <p>From regular backups and security monitoring to content updates and feature enhancements, I'm here to ensure your digital presence continues to serve you well long after launch.</p>
        <IconLink href="mailto:hello@kenchase.com?subject=Ken Chase web maintenance">Contact me for web maintenance</IconLink>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section id="client-list" classList="kc-region--lg" title="Partial Client List">
    <p>My clients include:</p>
    <ul class="column-list-2">
      {clientList.map((client) => <li> {client.name}</li>)}
    </ul>
  </Section>
</Layout>
